com.google.gcloud.bigquery

Class ExternalTableInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.BaseTableInfo
      • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.ExternalTableInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ExternalTableInfo
extends BaseTableInfo
    Google BigQuery External Table information. BigQuery's external tables are tables whose data reside outside of BigQuery but can be queried as normal BigQuery tables. External tables are experimental and might be subject to change or removed.
    See Also:
    Federated Data Sources , Serialized Form
